-- Telesp Net Income Rises 10% to $393.5 Million in Second Quarter of 2010
-- Laura Price
-- 2010-07-28T11:38:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-28/telesp-net-income-rises-10-to-393-5-million-in-second-quarter-of-2010.html

          
          
             Telesp - Telecomunicacoes de Sao
Paulo SA, the Brazilian unit of Telefonica SA, posted net income
of 695.3 million reais in the second quarter.  
 Net profit in the year-earlier period was 630.3 million
reais, Telesp said in a regulatory filing today.  
